reviews.text: Great place for brunch and coffee. Good vegetarian options. Vegetarian burger had very light taste. Kids menu is also available.
Nice restaurant with good service. Food was tasty and served fresh. The atmosphere of the restaurant was good. Happy place
Very good service and high quality brunch menu that can be tailored to your needs, very tasty all round, coffee also very good 👍
餐廳食物不錯，雖然價格是中上價，對比食物質素、環境，是還可以接受。English breakfast有多款食物放在碟上，感覺是豐富。雞肉漢堡也不錯，有雞軟骨放在免冶雞肉内，最喜歡是薯條也是一絕，平時少吃也不禁吃多了。餐牌還有Egg Benedict, spaghetti, pizza等多款選擇。唯一部份waiter態度需要改進，除此以外，整個用餐感受是好的。
Good service, great menu
